Package: claude-signal
Version: 0.1.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: default-jre-headless | java17-runtime-headless, tmux (>= 3.0)
Maintainer: dmz006 <dmz006@github.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/dmz006/claude-signal
Description: Signal-to-Claude-Code bridge daemon
 claude-signal bridges Signal messenger group messages to claude-code
 AI coding sessions running in tmux. Message yourself to start coding
 tasks, receive async updates, and interact with sessions from anywhere.
 .
 Includes a Progressive Web App for real-time access via Tailscale.
